        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">From the SoL FAQ<BR>"Luclin is the name of the ringed moon that orbits Norrath which currently can only been seen via the Plane of Sky. We expect that Al`Kabor will soon pierce the veil of shadow that hides it from view elsewhere in Norrath."</P><P>So I guess that once the expansion is released we'll be able to see the moon from any zone</P><P>Fopa asked why the good chose dark and evil chose light. They probably ripped the idea from LE Modesitt's "Recluce" series of books. In those, black represents order and white represents chaos (black being pure, white being a combination of colours) </P><P></P><P>Narben the Gnomish Gnecro<BR>"There are people in this game that should have been strangled at birth"<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
