        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Black is the absence of all colors, it is representative of the negation of light. White is all colors combined.</P><P>So on the white side, you can't cast Quivering Veil of Xarn, but on the dark side, you can Levant in every zone.</P><P>That is... if the night time crap is consistent.</P><P><BR>Dadok (Rodcet Nife)</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
